firstly, in a large vessel boil enough water and add 1 cup penne pasta and ½ tsp salt.
masala pasta recipe
stir well and boil for 13 minutes or as mentioned in package.
masala pasta recipe
drain off the water once pasta turns al dente. keep aside.
masala pasta recipe
now in a large kadai heat 1 tsp oil and 1 tsp butter.
masala pasta recipe
saute in 1 inch ginger and 2 clove garlic.
masala pasta recipe
further saute ½ onion till they turn soft.
indian style pasta
additionally add 1 cup tomato pulp and saute well. to prepare tomato pulp, blend 3 tomatoes in mixi to form smooth puree.
indian style pasta
keep stirring till the tomato pulp thickens.
indian style pasta
now add ¼ tsp turmeric, ½ tsp chilli powder, ½ tsp garam masala and ½ tsp salt.
indian style pasta
saute till the spices gets cooked completely.
indian style pasta
now add 2 tbsp corn, ¼ capsicum, ¼ carrot, 2 tbsp peas and 7 florets broccoli. saute for a minute.
indian pasta recipes
add in 3 tbsp water and mix well.
indian pasta recipes
cover and simmer for 5 minutes or till vegetables get cooked well yet retain their shape.
indian pasta recipes
now add in 2 tbsp tomato sauce and ½ tsp mixed herbs. mix well.
indian pasta recipes
add in cooked pasta and mix gently till the sauce gets coated well.
indian pasta recipes
finally, serve masala pasta indian style hot topped with cheese if required.
